metadata.name: ETH Eggs Soon to Be Unveiled
metadata.description: ETH Eggs is a collection of 10000 randomly generated adorable eggs living on Ethereum Blockchain. They are fragile and need responsible holders to keep them safe. Each egg is a ticket to have a display stand in our Sandbox art gallery and to play Egg Escape, a P2E game to be released in the future. Join our Twitter and Discord for more information.
